ces simpler geometries and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"improves performance. The default value is 0.375."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionSimplificationTolerance"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoptionsimplificationtolerance","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterRadius":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterRadius","title":"MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterRadius","fragments":[{"text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterRadius","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSNumber"},{"type":"text","text":" object containing an integer; specifies the radius of each"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"cluster if clustering is enabled. A value of 512 produces a radius equal to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the width of a tile. The default value is 50."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoptionclusterradius","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","title":"MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSource/initWithIdentifier:URL:options:":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a shape source with an identifier, URL, and dictionary of options for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the source."}],"title":"initWithIdentifier:URL:options:","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource\/initWithIdentifier:URL:options:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/